                "definition": "The code element is used to indicate that Task is a request for data and whether the data request is a code, FHIR query syntax or a questionnaire.  The code element is a required element and must be populated with one of the following values: \"data-request-code\", \"data-request-query\",or \"data-request-questionnaire\".",
